dct_description_sm: Relief shown by shading and spot heights. "802127 (R00855) 3-93." Also issued folded to 25 x 14 cm. Includes text, location map, comparative area diagram, graph, and coat-of-arms. Ancillary maps: Land use -- Economic activity and natural resources -- Population -- Ethnic majorities -- Sarajevo and vicinity.
